description: Annehem Fastigheter AB owns and manages real properties. The company is headquartered in Solna, Stockholm and currently employs 15 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2020-12-11. The firm owns and manages commercial properties in Sweden, Finland and Norway. Annehem Fastigheter have both private companies and public institutions as its clients. The firm is focused on growing the portfolio through property acquisitions and management of existing portfolio.
